THE FOLLOWING CANDIDATE S HAVE SECURED 50% OR ABOVE MARKS IN THE FIRST MCQs TEST FOR THE POST OF CIVIL JUDGE & JUDICIAL MAGISTRATE HELD ON 20TH MARCH, 2022 AND DECLARED ELIGIBLE FOR SECOND WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST:-

LIST OF CANDIDATES ELIGIBLE FOR SECOND

WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST New

NOTE:THE SECOND WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST FOR THE POST OF CIVIL JUDGE & JUDICIAL MAGISTRATE IS SCHEDULED TO BE HELD ON SUNDAY, 08TH MAY, 2022 AT 10:00 A.M. AT THE LAWN OF SINDH HIGH COURT, KARACHI, WHICH WILL BE CONDUCTED BY SIBA TESTING SERVICE (STS). THE REPORTING TIME FOR TEST IS 9:00 A.M. AND NO CANDIDATE SHALL BE PERMITTED TO ENTER IN THE EXAMINATION HALL AFTER 9:30 A.M. ALL CANDIDATES ARE REQUIRED TO BRING TEST LETTER AND ORIGINAL C.N.I.C. ANY CANDIDATE NOT IN POSSESSION OF ORIGINAL C.N.I.C. WILL NOT BE ALLOWED TO ENTER THE EXAMINATION HALL.

THE ELIGIBLE CANDIDATES WHO HAVE SECURED 50% OR ABOVE MARKS IN THE FIRST MCQs TEST HELD ON 20.03.2022 ARE INFORMED THAT THEY CAN DOWNLOAD THE TEST CALL LETTERS OF SECOND WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST FROM FOLLOWING LINK MENTIONED BELOW:

Block Wise List of Candidates for 2nd Written Subjective Test of Civil Judges & Judicial Magistrate New

FOR ANY QUERY: 021-99203151- 57 EXT: 352

THE RESULT OF FIRST PRELIMINARY TEST FOR THE POST OF CIVIL JUDGE & JUDICIAL MAGISTRATE HELD ON SUNDAY, 20th MARCH, 2022 IN THE LAWN OF SINDH HIGH COURT AT KARACHI, HAS BEEN ANNOUNCED BY SUKKUR IBA TESTING SERVICE (STS) AND CAN BE SEEN BY VISITING THE FOLLOWING LINK:-

RESULT OF FIRST PRELIMINARY TEST FOR THE POST OF CIVIL JUDGE & JUDICIAL MAGISTRATE New

THE CANDIDATES WHO APPREARED IN THE FIRST PRELIMINARY TEST MAY APPLY FOR RECHECKING/RECOUNTING OF MARKS, AND MAY SEND THEIR APPLICATION DIRECTLY TO SUKKUR IBA TESTING SERVICE (STS) FOR ACTION AT THEIR END, (IF SO DESIRE.) INSTEAD OF SENDING THEIR APPLICATION TO THIS COURT.

THE FOLLOWING CANDIDATES HAVE SECURED 60% OR ABOVE MARKS IN THE FIRST PRELIMINARY TEST FOR THE POST OF ADDITIONAL DISTRICT & SESSIONS JUDGE HELD ON 7th MARCH, 2021 AND DECLARED ELIGIBLE FOR SECOND WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST :-

ELIGIBLE CANDIDATES FOR SECOND WRITTEN SUBJECTIVE TEST

THE SECOND SUBJECTIVE TEST WILL BE HELD ON SATURDAY, 10th APRIL, 2021 AT 10:00 A.M. (REPORTING TIME 09:00 A.M.) AND SUNDAY, 11th APRIL, 2021 AT 10:00 A.M. (REPORTING TIME 09:00 A.M.) AT 5TH FLOOR, NEW ANNEXE BUILDING OF ADMINISTRATION BLOCK, HIGH COURT OF SINDH, KARACHI. THE TEST WILL BE COMPRISED ON TWO PAPERS OF 100 MARKS EACH OF 3 HOURS DURATION WHICH WILL BE TERMED AS PAPER-I AND PAPER-II.

THE CANDIDATES ARE INFORMED THAT THE SECOND TEST CALL LETTERS ARE ONLINE AVAILABLE, WHICH CAN BE DOWNLOADED FROM

http://shc.gov.pk/admitcard.php (Closed)

FOR ANY QUIERY 021-99203151- 57 EXT.352.
